# Design system

- Tokens and theme: `src/styles.css` (`@theme inline`, risk semantic colors, `--font-display`, `--font-mono`).
- Fonts: Instrument Serif (display), Geist Sans (UI), JetBrains Mono (data) — linked in `__root.tsx`.
- Use existing utility classes: `font-display`, `font-mono-data`, risk tokens from the spec.
- shadcn primitives in `src/components/ui/` — customize via CSS variables, don't replace with one-off styles.
- Landing components: `src/components/landing/`. App features: `src/components/app/`.
- Motion: restrained; prefer `Reveal` patterns on marketing pages. No gratuitous animation.
- Empty/in-progress app surfaces: `PlaceholderPanel` until the phase ships real UI.
